title: The Fantastic Four: First Steps | H.E.R.B.I.E. Behind The Scenes | Now Playing In Theaters

author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
This week, Marvel Studios’ The Fantastic Four: First Steps Director Matt Shakman, stars Pedro Pascal, Vanessa Kirby, Joseph Quinn, Ebon Moss-Bachrach, Ralph Ineson, Julia Garner, and Paul Walter Hauser share spoilers from the film. Plus, Marvel Animation’s Eyes of Wakanda Showrunner Todd Harris discusses what viewers can expect from this new chapter of the warriors of Wakanda.

00:00 - Welcome Back!
1:11 - Matt Shakman, Pedro Pascal, Vanessa Kirby, Joseph Quinn, Ebon Moss-Bachrach, Ralph Ineson, Julia Garner, and Paul Walter Hauser talk spoilers
12:54 - Marvel Animation’s Eyes of Wakanda Showrunner Todd Harris on new chapter for Wakanda
